'''Otomo no Tabito''' (&#22823;&#20276;&#26053;&#20154; ''Otomo no Tabito''; ) was a [[Japan]]ese poet of an old time, best known as the father of [[Otomo no Yakamochi]], who contributed to compiling [[Manyoshu]] alongside the father.

{{stub}}
